examples.en: We all jumped in a taxi.
He jumped off the roof.
He jumped on his opponent.
The car jumped the curb.
He jumped into the pool.
He jumped into the game.
Three cars had jumped the rails.
He was jumped into buying the house.
examples.ru: Его обманом заставили купить этот дом.

examples.en: The guests all jumped at the invitation.
She jumped to an early lead in the race.
examples.ru: Она рано захватила лидерство в гонке.

examples.en: He jumped his horse.
Prices jumped overnight.
The child jumped into bed.
The runner jumped a hurdle.
The dog jumped onto the sofa.
Everyone jumped into the pool.
She jumped to her feet and left.
examples.ru: Она вскочила на ноги и ушла.

examples.en: The cat jumped down off the table.
Matt jumped up to answer the phone.
examples.ru: Мэтт вскочил, чтобы ответить на телефонный звонок.

examples.en: Marcia jumped. 'What's that noise?'
He jumped into his car and sped off.
examples.ru: Он прыгнул в машину и умчался.

examples.en: He jumped over the wall and ran off.
examples.ru: Он перепрыгнул через стену и убежал.

examples.en: The cheerleaders jumped and twirled.
examples.ru: Участницы группы поддержки /чирлидеры/ прыгали и кружились.

examples.en: We came to a stream and jumped over.
examples.ru: Мы пришли к ручью и перепрыгнули через него.

examples.en: They jumped in the car and sped away.
examples.ru: Они прыгнули в машину и умчались.

examples.en: The dog jumped up and licked her face.
examples.ru: Пёс подпрыгнул и лизнул её в лицо.

examples.en: The circus lion jumped through the hoop.
Norway jumped from ninth to third place.
examples.ru: Норвегия перескочила с девятого места на третье.

examples.en: Brenda jumped in the car and zoomed off.
examples.ru: Бренда запрыгнула в машину и смылась.

examples.en: He jumped into his truck and drove away.
examples.ru: Он вскочил в свой грузовик и уехал.
